Deploy, install, integrate, maintain, and administer systems including hardware, software, and configurations. Lead the planning, life-cycle management, and development for systems. Provide decision making, leadership, and coaching or mentoring to others in a group. Demonstrate strong communication skills and ability to thrive in a collaborative and independent environment.
